testName: Purpose Specification  
criterias:
  - criteriaName: The company clearly discloses why it collects, aggregates and shares user information.
    indicators:
      - indicator: >-
          The company clearly discloses its purpose for collecting user information.
          The company clearly discloses its purpose for sharing user information.
          The company clearly discloses the purpose for combining user information from various services (if it does combine).
        procedures:
          - >-
            Investigation and analysis of publicly available documentation to
            determine what the company clearly discloses.
            
testName: Limitation on Information Use and Sharing
criterias:
  - criteriaName: The company clearly discloses that it limits use of information to specified purposes.   
    indicators:
      - indicator: >-
          The company clearly discloses that it limits its use of user information to the purposes for which it was collected.
          The company clearly discloses that it will obtain consent if it uses user information for additional purposes, for which it was not collected. 
          The company clearly discloses that it shares user information as is reasonably necessary for the service to work. 
          
        procedures:
          - >-
            Investigation and analysis of publicly available documentation to
            determine what the company clearly discloses.
